title: Uniclife Lockable Storage Box with Combination Lock 13 L Large Medicine Lock Box for Home Office and School Fridge Lock Box Stackable Locking Container Bin for Personal Items Phones Food & Snacks
features: Lockable Storage Box: Large lock box effectively isolates mobile phones, tablets, gaming devices, TV remotes, toys, calorie-rich food or snacks, cigarettes, etc. Perfect solution to help your family develop better habits and strengthen self-discipline

Secure Combination Lock: No unauthorized access! The 3-digit coded lock on the locking container provides 1,000 possible combinations. Easily set or update the code at any time, ensuring your exclusive access and keeping the items properly stored

Reliable PP5 Material: The robust combination lock box reliably withstands temperatures from -0.4 °F to 332.6 °F (-18 °C to 167 °C). Ideal for use as a desk organizer or fridge lock box! Its transparent walls allow you to check the contents at a glance

3.5-Gallon Large Capacity: Outer size: 11.8" L x 9.5" W x 8" H. Perfectly accommodate personal items, medicines, canned beverages, knives, sharp hand tools, or even jewelry and cash. A must-have for every family, office, school, retail store, and more

Easy to Use: Only simple assembly required – insert the 4 side panels into the base and attach the cover. (NOTE: Non-detachable once assembled!) The medicine lock box is also stackable. No more clutter or waste of valuable floor and countertop space
